headline: Generac Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call
summary: WAUKESHA, Wis., April 16, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Generac Holdings Inc. ("Generac") (NYSE: GNRC), a leading global designer, manufacturer, and provider of energy technology solutions and other power products, today announced plans to release its first quarter 2025 financial results before the market opens on Wednesday, April 30, 2025.
